Megaton looked at Prowl, the weapon looked like a pea shooter to the giant.
(Does Prowl still look like his owl body or did it change when he got the
new beast mode?)

"I am Megaton, destined leader of the Predacons." The mutant folded his
wings in front of him for extra protection and a show of nonhostility. He
glanced around the battlefield watching the gathering maximals. "The
predacon files were incomplete" he thinks realizeing that most of the bots
present weren't mentioned.

From:  Yanshosh@a...
Date:  Mon Mar 19, 2001 10:11pm
Subject:  Re: New Battle at CF


::Prowl::

He exits the Cybertronian Fire, aiming his weapons at Megaton.

"Identify yourself!" Prowl says, ready for battle once again, only
this time he knew that in extreme cases he could transform into the
giant beast that he had gotten from Iron Raptor.
